conditionals5.caption:
Which of the following alternatives for MISSING_CODE1 and MISSING_CODE2 will print 2 and 3.

I.
MISSING_CODE1: x or z
MISSING_CODE2: y and not x

II.
MISSING_CODE1: not y
MISSING_CODE2: x or y

III.
MISSING_CODE1: x and y
MISSING_CODE2: y and z

IV.
MISSING_CODE1: x and not y
MISSING_CODE2: not z and y
